        <section name="Building from Source">
            <p>Force Field X can be built from source using Apache ANT and a Java Development Kit (JDK).</p>
            <p>The following tools are required:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Ant 1.7.1</li>
                <li>JDK 1.6.0</li>
            </ul>
            <subsection name="Directory Structure">
                <p>The build files assume the following directory structure:</p>
                <source>
|-- FFX
    |-- lib 
    |-- native
    |-- test
                </source>
            </subsection>
        </section>
    </body>
